    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>You know how to get lost in a crowd and hide among it, moving like fluid within its ranks and losing yourself in the bustle. You can use cover from crowds to Hide and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.VMozDqMMuK5kpoX4]{Sneak}, gaining a +2 circumstance bonus on your Stealth checks when in a crowd of at least 10 creatures and a +4 circumstance bonus on your Stealth checks when in a crowd of at least 100 creatures. Hidden creatures do not count as members of a crowd. Halve the number of creatures required to get these bonuses if you are a master in Deception.</p>"
